  "detailed_description": "Simple RTS is a Simple Real-Time-Strategy Game Like in the good old days, with 20 types of units<br><br>The goal is simply to conquer all territories on the map, which is also your AI opponent's goal...<br><br>The main features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Looks like Dune2, Feels like Z & Tower Defense (very dynamic and stressful)<br></li><li>Well balanced units<br></li><li>Helpful mini-map <br></li><li>Resources gathering <br></li><li>Accuracy bonus for units on higher ground<br></li><li>Units are leveling up for each kill</li></ul><br>Some cool examples of special units in the game:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Invisible bike to spy enemy territories<br></li><li>Tank that can teleport to any location on the map<br></li><li>Artillery that bombs any chosen area on the map<br></li><li>Rocket launcher that converts the enemy to join your side<br></li><li>And more surprises...</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Simple RTS is a Simple Real-Time-Strategy Game Like in the good old days, with 20 types of units<br><br>The goal is simply to conquer all territories on the map, which is also your AI opponent's goal...<br><br>The main features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Looks like Dune2, Feels like Z & Tower Defense (very dynamic and stressful)<br></li><li>Well balanced units<br></li><li>Helpful mini-map <br></li><li>Resources gathering <br></li><li>Accuracy bonus for units on higher ground<br></li><li>Units are leveling up for each kill</li></ul><br>Some cool examples of special units in the game:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Invisible bike to spy enemy territories<br></li><li>Tank that can teleport to any location on the map<br></li><li>Artillery that bombs any chosen area on the map<br></li><li>Rocket launcher that converts the enemy to join your side<br></li><li>And more surprises...</li></ul>",
